        <item>
            <title>Tesla Cybertruck 下週四正式交付　最新車廂內外照片</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/26/tesla-cybertruck-officially-launched-next-thursday/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-cybertruck-officially-launched-next-thursday</link>
