            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蔣納偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 14:30:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[車壇動向]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Cybertruck]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1206308</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Tesla Cybertruck 將於下週 11 月 30 日正式交付，剛好是該原型車首次公開亮相的四年後。Tesla 將於下週四開始向客戶交付其首款電動卡車，並有望宣佈諸如電池和驅動系統規格、性能和續航數據以及價格等細節。</p><p>發佈前，已有關於 Cybertruck 的新照片和影片由小紅書用戶發佈，並持續在線上流傳，展示了白色飾板版本，包括觸摸屏用戶界面（UI）、方形方向盤、巨大的中控台、運動座椅和玻璃車頂等。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1206341 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXYAATQVv.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲網上流傳圖片</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1206344 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTcWQAAwEtz.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" />▲其中一張照片拍攝了觸摸螢幕的顯示器，揭示了部分菜單。可看到後蓋（開/關）、懸掛設置（進入/低/高）、方向盤和後視鏡調節、頭燈、兒童鎖、窗口鎖、哨兵模式、洗車模式等控制項。（網上流傳圖片）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1206347 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTYW4AAIMOI.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前座椅擁有側向支撐和穿孔材料，可見其配備了通風和加熱功能。（網上流傳圖片）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1206350 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkKTbXQAAWcG5.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲帶蓋子打開的前行李箱的照片，顯示出其容量。（網上流傳圖片）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1206354 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYXMAAADrx.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三角形的側鏡蓋和擋風玻璃雨刷。（網上流傳圖片）</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1206356 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/F_bkQWYW8AAt_dA.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲還有一張從前方拍攝的 Cybertruck 行駛中的照片。（網上流傳圖片）</p><p>據瞭解，本週 Tesla 還在其展廳放置的廣告海報上透露，Cybertruck 的牽引能力為 11,000 磅，載重為 2,500 磅。</p><p>橫幅還提到，Cybertruck 的車牀由超堅固的片狀模塑複合材料（SMC）製成，玻璃具有抗破裂性，而且擁有超硬不銹鋼外骨骼，所有這些特性共同使其成為「世界上最堅固的卡車」。</p><p>根據 Tesla 產品設計總監 Javier Verdura 的説法，屆時 11 月 30 日會向客戶交付首批 Cybertruck，相信會有更多關於 Cybertruck 的資訊曝光。交付活動將在德州 Gigafactory 舉行，但可能只有 10 輛車會在此次活動中交付。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://insideevs.com/news/697558/tesla-cybertruck-leaked-photos-provide-best-look-yet-inside-out/">insideevs</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

